<div id="block-usps-power-your-career-parablock" class="usps-paralib-hide-label usps-show-as-section settings-tray-editable block block-entity-block block-entity-blockparagraphs-library-item" data-drupal-settingstray="editable">
  
    
      
            <div class="field field--name-label field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Power Your Career</div>
      
            <div class="field field--name-paragraphs field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__item">    
  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--media-block-extended paragraph--view-mode--default">
        

            <div class="grid-col-fill">
            <div class="grid-container mediablock-ext">
      <div class="grid-row mediablock-ext-record">
        <div class="grid-col-12 tablet:grid-col-auto mediablock-ext-left-col">
                      
            <div class="field field--name-field-mediablock-ext-img field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><article class="media media--type-remote-video media--view-mode-default">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-field-media-oembed-video field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item"><iframe src="/media/oembed?url=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3Dr2gXL6Va5KM&amp;max_width=0&amp;max_height=0&amp;hash=qL5aIbzSjUVqd3hy_UIFZRnRMNQxSqSG37dHFPoSNDc" frameborder="0" allowtransparency width="200" height="113" class="media-oembed-content" title="USPS OIG - Who We Are"></iframe>
</div>
      
  </article>
</div>
      
                  </div>
        <div class="grid-col-12 tablet:grid-col mediablock-ext-right-col">
                    <div class="grid-row mediablock-ext-summary-row">
            <div class="grid-col-fill mediablock-ext-summary-col">
            <h4>Who We Are</h4>
            <p>With six government organizations bearing the term “postal” in their name, there’s bound to be some confusion! Our charge to guard the United States postal system against fraud, waste, and abuse is unique. In just over two minutes, this video captures our mission as we work to safeguard the integrity and efficiency of the nation’s postal system. Like, share, and follow for more!</p>

            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-row mediablock-ext-link-row">
            <div class="grid-col-fill mediablock-ext-link-col">
              <a class="usa-button" href="https://youtu.be/r2gXL6Va5KM">LEARN MORE</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
